      "end": 1.68,
      "text": "This is a LibraVox recording.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-001",
      "start": 2.7,
      "end": 5.16,
      "text": "All LibraVox recordings are in the public domain.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-002",
      "start": 6.08,
      "end": 11.12,
      "text": "For more information or to volunteer, please visit LibraVox.org.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-003",
      "start": 11.7,
      "end": 15.7,
      "text": "Recorded by Christine Doer, the known as Assah, Florida.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-004",
      "start": 17.46,
      "end": 20.7,
      "text": "A Subspables, the Viper, and the File.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-005",
      "start": 22.38,
      "end": 26.96,
      "text": "A Viper entered a carpenter's shop and went from one to another of the tools, begging",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 26.96,
      "end": 28.04,
      "text": "for something to eat.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 28.88,
      "end": 33.98,
      "text": "Among the rest, he addressed himself to the file and asked for the favor of a meal.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-008",
      "start": 34.9,
      "end": 37.8,
      "text": "The file replied in a tone of pity and contempt,",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-009",
      "start": 38.66,
      "end": 42.92,
      "text": "what a simpleton you must be if you imagine you will get anything from me",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-010",
      "start": 43.48,
      "end": 47.74,
      "text": "who invariably take from everyone and never give anything in return.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-011",
      "start": 49.0,
      "end": 50.96,
      "text": "The covetous are poor givers.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
